	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"You wish to harness the dark arts you've witnessed from those around you? Or perhaps you've found a scroll that piqued your interest. Either way, I welcome you into my dark embrace."
				"&6Goety: The Dark Arts&r is a magic mod with a focus on dark or black magic. You as the caster utilize &6&osoul energy&r and wield &6&ofocuses&r to cast a variety of different spells."
				"Now then, follow me, my new apprentice. We have much to learn."
			]
			id: "09A68ADF45EC8501"
