		{
			dependencies: ["09A68ADF45EC8501"]
			description: [
				"&6&oSoul Energy&r is the driving force of the dark arts, so naturally, your first step as a fledgling caster is to harness this energy for yourself. To do this, a &o&6totem&r will be required. The craft the &6&ototem of roots&r, &oectoplasm&r is required. There are many ways to obtain it, but for yourself, I suggest seeking out a &4&owraith&r."
				"{image:modpack:textures/wraith.png width:156 height:90 align:center}"
			]
