		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5981B3DEDD0B3827"]
			description: [
				"There are two other components we will want to acquire. One of those are &6&ofabrics&r. Made from lapis and some string, a variety of different fabrics can be created by adding one addition ingredient. These all have their purposes, but for ours, we will want &o&6magic fabric&r, made by adding gold to the recipe."
				"{image:modpack:textures/fabrics.png width:156 height:90 align:center}"
			]
