		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2BED66945BBA3836"]
			description: [
				"Now that you've obtained an empty focus, perhaps multiple, it is time to combine it with your earlier magic fabric, some wooden planks, and 2 pieces of Lapis Lazuli. In doing this, you will craft your main tool, the &o&6Dark Wand&r."
				"This will server as your primary method of casting magic. In the future, you may wish to upgrade it, but that is out of the scope for these first lessons. Once fitted with a &ofocus&r, you need but hold the wand in your hands and right click, as if using any other tools or weapons."
			]
			id: "3873AB1F19921EF0"
