		{
			dependencies: ["08E9141026F7F288"]
			description: [
				"As I said before, there are two components we will want to acquire. The second of these is an &6&oempty focus&r. For now, the simplest method of obtaining one would be to use your totem and some amethyst. Once you have that, then we can begin."
				"{image:modpack:textures/empty-focus.png width:156 height:90 align:center}"
