		{
			dependencies: ["5981B3DEDD0B3827"]
			description: [
				"You've made your totem, now you must fill it. Fortunately, doing so is a simple matter. Merely killing mobs while a totem is either in your hotbar or equipped as a curio will fill the totem with that mob's energy. Different types of mobs have differing amounts of soul energy, with undead being one of the weakest, most likely due to their nature."
				"The Totem of Roots can hold a max of &o&6100 souls&r. Before continuing, I suggest you fill it, as we will be needing that energy very soon."
			]
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
			icon: "goety:ectoplasm"
			id: "2AEACBC0748148A7"
			optional: true
