		{
			dependencies: ["3873AB1F19921EF0"]
			description: [
				"You've obtained your wand at last, but you should not go off trying to cast a spell so quickly. To do so, one requires &6&oa focus&r. There are many different focuses, but a simple one to start with is the &o&6Soul Light Focus&r. With some sticks, coal of any kind, and an empty focus, you will be able to create it."
				"Now armed with a focus, inset it into your wand with the appropriate binding (Default: Z). You can now cast the spell and shoot a projectile that upon hitting a surface with leave a small but ever present light."
				"{image:modpack:textures/soul-light.png width:156 height:90 align:center}"
			]
			id: "7DC5F505120655C1"
			rewards: [
				{
					amount: 100L
					currency: "eternalcurrencies:ancientcoins"
					id: "1EBFD7CA9D343E7F"
