				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Soul Light, Soul Bright"
			x: -1.0d
			y: -2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["7DC5F505120655C1"]
			description: [
				"You've created a powerful utility in the Soul Light Focus, but if you wish to take things further, then we shall look at creating a &o&6Soul Bolt Focus&r. This focus serves as a simple projectile, and not much more. Still, it can be amplified later through enchantments and powerful items. You will need some arrows and ectoplasm, along with the Soul Light Focus you crafted earlier. I also recommend making a second Soul Light Focus, as to not strip away a useful tool to gain a weapon."
				""
				"{image:modpack:textures/soul-bolt.png width:156 height:90 align:center}"
			]
