			dependencies: ["7D6F2EC87AA8F366"]
			description: [
				"With this, we have come to the end of our introduction. The Dark Arts will now open for you. Many powerful artifacts and spells lay there, waiting to be discovered. &8Necromancy&r, &2Nature&r, &1The Abyss&r, &bWinds&r, &eStorms&r, &dGeomancy&r."
